Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.04,0:00:49.53,nhkop,Comment,0,0,0,,Tokei no hari ga tomatta jikan wo nurikaete
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.35,0:00:57.25,nhkop,Comment,0,0,0,,Sashinobeta ryoute kamiawanai pazuru
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.12,0:01:06.19,nhkop,Comment,0,0,0,,Okizari ni shiteta futari deau made
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.20,0:01:10.50,nhkop,Comment,0,0,0,,Nakushiteta nani ka
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.50,0:01:18.77,nhkop,Comment,0,0,0,,Saigo no kakera wo torimodoshite
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.21,0:01:24.61,nhkop,Comment,0,0,0,,Aruki dasou
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.39,0:01:42.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This sun is awfully hot for 9:00 in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.17,0:01:51.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But even so, this is just the thing\nto refresh my rotted brain.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.71,0:02:00.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm going to be reborn, starting today.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.42,0:02:02.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's a revolution!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.79,0:02:09.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,One to keep this girl smiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.55,0:02:25.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\c&H524738&\shad0\fscx42.5\fscy41.25\3c&HFFFFF8&\move(275,122,282,120,0,3470)}Shin Yoko Minato Station
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.68,0:02:34.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's beginning,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.88,0:02:36.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,my journey with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.62,0:02:41.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's a new departure for just the two of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.16,0:02:49.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What the... What's up with that gloomy group?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.70,0:02:52.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's ominous, for a new departure on a clear day.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.50,0:02:55.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sorry to keep you waiting. Shall we go?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.97,0:02:57.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.04,0:03:02.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Uh, hold on, Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.15,0:03:10.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm Hana-Hana.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.72,0:03:12.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So, she knows these people?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.99,0:03:17.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\alpha&H60&}Uh, this is a guy I knew from high school,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.59,0:03:17.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And what's this "Hana-Hana" stuff?\NAnd she was meeting them here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.69,0:03:20.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And we're not taking a vacation just the two of us?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.69,0:03:19.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\alpha&H60&}And when I told him about today"s "Off" meeting,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.66,0:03:21.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\alpha&H60&}He said he wanted to take part.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.83,0:03:21.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.80,0:03:23.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Right, Sato?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.73,0:03:25.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.24,0:03:29.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.24,0:03:34.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So, this is that guy, the one you\ntalked about on the forum.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.84,0:03:37.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes, it's him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.55,0:03:44.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I guess it's all right. Well, shall we get going?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.13,0:03:55.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sato?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.23,0:03:56.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh? Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.92,0:04:18.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\c&HD9B6C7&\3c&HFFEAFF&\shad0\fnSegoe Print\frz14.319\pos(153,69)}Akira Jogasaki
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.13,0:04:18.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\shad0\fnSegoe Print\frz14.319\c&HC7BCC1&\3c&HFFFDFE&\pos(204,121)}Akira Jogasaki
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.97,0:04:38.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sorry to keep you waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.85,0:04:51.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh, wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.19,0:04:53.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This boat belongs to you, Mr. Minegishi?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.76,0:04:57.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's the first time I've been on one of these, Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.29,0:05:01.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So, you really did own a cabin cruiser.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.10,0:05:04.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Would you rather I'd been lying?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.24,0:05:10.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If it were a lie, the off meeting\nitself would be called off.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.84,0:05:12.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.51,0:05:16.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?\NWe've come all this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.28,0:05:18.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We can't call it off now!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.32,0:05:25.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're absolutely right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.69,0:05:30.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let's hurry up and go to this island of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.57,0:06:15.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Uh, Senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.50,0:06:16.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.37,0:06:22.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There are parts of our talk last night\nthat I don't remember exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.41,0:06:24.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Where was it we're going again?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.48,0:06:27.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,An uninhabited island.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.62,0:06:28.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.48,0:06:37.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's an island privately owned by "Mr. God",\NI guess his real name is Mr. Minegishi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.89,0:06:42.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He says it has a very lovely sandy beach
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.13,0:06:45.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and it's just like Paradise.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.84,0:06:51.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,An appropriate place for us now, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.21,0:07:00.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I don't need it anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.55,0:07:02.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.45,0:07:07.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.76,0:07:13.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\fnSegoe Print\shad0\bord0\c&HADA5A4&\frz4.099\pos(187,183)}Hitomi
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.53,0:07:20.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Mr. Jogasaki, we're ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.97,0:07:22.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.94,0:07:30.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,All right, hit it for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.69,0:07:40.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah, bingo.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.16,0:07:46.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This means we should be able to\nwrap this up today, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.43,0:07:49.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's a bit early, but let's all grab lunch together.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.36,0:07:51.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We'll take care of the rest ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.33,0:07:54.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's left is all simple work,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.64,0:07:57.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,so there's no need for you to use up your time\nlooking over it, Mr. Jogasaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.84,0:08:00.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You have plans with your girlfriend, right?
