Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.82,0:09:19.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ah, Hitomi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.85,0:09:26.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The cellular phone you are calling is either in a\nlocale without cellular service or is turned off.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.27,0:09:38.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Uh, we placed a reservation recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.18,0:09:43.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.04,0:09:46.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No, if it's been cancelled, that's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.98,0:09:49.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sorry for the trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.59,0:09:59.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,An Introduction to\nthe Study of Poisons
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.08,0:10:20.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There's a dock here and everything, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.22,0:10:23.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Apparently, a wealthy capitalist once\nhad a summer home here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.75,0:10:28.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I bought it from his relatives who put\nit up for an internet auction.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.56,0:10:30.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.87,0:10:38.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It really is amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.77,0:10:42.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I've never seen a real private beach before!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.67,0:10:48.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's a revolution!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.08,0:10:54.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.92,0:11:01.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ah, it feels good.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.29,0:11:05.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The only ones here are Senpai\nand those other three.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.03,0:11:08.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I don't have to be afraid of strangers looking at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.70,0:11:11.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It truly is Paradise.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.37,0:11:21.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You mustn't! Absolutely not!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.98,0:11:33.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I, too, tentatively declare I'll participate.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.02,0:11:36.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I plan to drink at a high-school\nfriend's place tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.56,0:11:38.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I decided a little while ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.63,0:11:43.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I haven't contacted him yet, but since he's\nhikikomori, it's for certain he's home.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.37,0:11:48.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I've known him a long time, so I have to say\ngoodbye to him beforehand anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.24,0:11:52.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\c&H32312F&\shad0\bord0\pos(204,109)}Address: 202 Mita House,\NKawasaki City, Kanagawa Prefecture
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.07,0:11:53.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I apologize if I drink too much and I'm late.\NYou can leave without me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.78,0:11:57.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh! Hot-hot-hot-hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.78,0:12:01.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh? You're not going to swim?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.48,0:12:08.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sorry, seems like last night's\nalcohol is still with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.18,0:12:32.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's the story with these guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.35,0:12:35.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Coming all this way to the beach\nand not even swimming...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.32,0:12:39.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Isn't an off meeting a place to be\nmore rowdy and have fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.15,0:12:42.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This is nothing but a group of hikikomori people.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.69,0:12:45.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Although, that includes me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.73,0:12:48.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No! This summer I'll be reborn.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.93,0:12:51.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes! It's a revolution!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.43,0:12:57.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,First thing is to make friendly talk\nwith the people I just met today.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.27,0:13:01.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's a high-level technique a hikikomori\ncouldn't possibly pull off.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.31,0:13:06.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Uh, hi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.38,0:13:08.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He ignored me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.82,0:13:13.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No, no, New Sato isn't going to be discouraged\nby something like being ignored once.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.06,0:13:19.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What game are you playing? I play a lot too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.36,0:13:21.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I play gal-games though.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.30,0:13:26.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I have a younger friend who knows all about games;\nhe's a real game otaku... Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.07,0:13:29.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.04,0:13:33.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Did I say something inappropriate?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.68,0:13:37.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No, no, New Sato doesn't get discouraged\nby this kind of stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.48,0:13:39.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I've had a revolution after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.45,0:13:42.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Here goes, I'll get it this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.95,0:13:45.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.49,0:13:52.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No, no, I assumed I'd get that sort of reaction.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.66,0:13:54.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Relax, New Sato.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.76,0:13:58.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Senpai told me before that you're\na medical student.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.43,0:14:02.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm a former medical student.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.00,0:14:03.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I don't attend school anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.11,0:14:08.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oops, that may have been a touchy subject.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.21,0:14:12.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Since I said that, I'll expose\nsomething shameful about myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.18,0:14:16.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah, the fact is, I'm hikikomori.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.75,0:14:17.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?\NYeah, the fact is, I'm hikikomori.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.32,0:14:17.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?\NI don't suppose there's some medicine\nthat could make me feel super-energetic?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.99,0:14:21.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I don't suppose there's some medicine\nthat could make me feel super-energetic?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.42,0:14:25.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If you have some, I'd love for\nyou to share it with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.56,0:14:27.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you stupid or what?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.33,0:14:30.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If I gave you that potent a medicine\nwithout a prescription,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.67,0:14:32.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,it'd be a violation of the pharmaceutical laws.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.37,0:14:35.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Either way, there's no medicine\nto cure a hikikomori.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.30,0:14:41.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He really doesn't have to talk as bluntly as that\nwhen somebody's just trying to be friendly.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.74,0:14:43.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Is there still something you want to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.12,0:14:49.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well, I don't necessarily have to talk to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.68,0:14:51.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I have other people to talk to.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.02,0:14:58.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah! That older guy will talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.83,0:15:08.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Relax, Sato, it's a revolution.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.07,0:15:09.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Will you drink one?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.35,0:15:25.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're amazing, Mr. Minegishi,\nwith that boat and this island.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.89,0:15:28.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.93,0:15:35.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How can a person acquire stuff like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.30,0:15:37.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,As someone with life experience, please tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.47,0:15:40.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's the point of asking that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.74,0:15:43.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The... The point...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.01,0:15:50.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's true I've acquired things ordinary\npeople couldn't acquire.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.31,0:15:55.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But in exchange, I lost so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.95,0:15:58.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Like an ordinary person's happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.85,0:16:01.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Do you still want to ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.99,0:16:04.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Uh, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.29,0:16:06.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's not that I wanted that desperately to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.89,0:16:08.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ex... Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.50,0:16:12.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.43,0:16:14.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,With this many human beings around...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.00,0:16:21.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,why am I so Ionely?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.11,0:16:26.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Even though I came all the way out\nto this island paradise...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.05,0:16:29.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,...even though it's our last Culture Festival!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.95,0:16:34.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wait, I wonder if that's also how the\NClass Rep felt back then?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.49,0:16:39.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Please be quiet! Homeroom isn't finished yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.59,0:16:41.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\alpha&H55&}This is our last Culture Festival, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.23,0:16:44.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I remember that was the time we were deciding\nwhat to put out for the Culture Festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.86,0:16:45.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\alpha&H55&}So, let's all make it an amazing one that"ll be a great memory!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.90,0:16:48.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,My noisy classmates were ignoring the Class Rep,\nwho was struggling all by herself,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.84,0:16:51.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and I was among them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.81,0:16:54.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What are you so worked up about all alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.21,0:16:55.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Is that the assertiveness of youth?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.84,0:16:57.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're a joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.11,0:17:03.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,At the time, I thought it was cooler to be detached.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.55,0:17:10.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I was detached toward studying,\ntoward romance, toward friendship...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.99,0:17:13.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And the conclusion of all that was\nlife as a hikikomori, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.88,0:17:40.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\c&HFDB2A9&\shad0\3c&H954E49&\frx14\fry34\frz349.43\pos(246,68)}Mita House
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.73,0:17:53.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sato! Get up, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.87,0:17:55.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's already past noon!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.54,0:17:57.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sato, hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.10,0:17:58.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The first day of the Comic Stall is gonna be over!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.97,0:18:00.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sato!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.58,0:18:04.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn it! I can't believe\NI overslept on this crucial day!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.25,0:18:09.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You... You're that girl Sato knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.52,0:18:11.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Uh, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.39,0:18:12.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.05,0:18:15.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Did Sato come back?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.66,0:18:18.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What? Did Sato go out?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.13,0:18:24.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Stop joking around, please. He's a hikikomori.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.97,0:18:28.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There's no way he could go all alone to a place with\nso many people like the Comic Stall, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.27,0:18:32.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He wasn't alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.57,0:18:34.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He went with a woman in a car.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.81,0:18:38.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That was somebody else you saw.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.88,0:18:41.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There's no way he has anyone like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.28,0:18:42.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.88,0:18:44.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No, hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.15,0:18:46.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There is one person.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.12,0:18:48.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If it were Hitomi Kashiwa who used\nto be in the Literature Club,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.52,0:18:50.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,he might go off somewhere with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.42,0:18:52.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Is what you just said true?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.03,0:18:59.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Would you be willing to tell me\na few more specifics?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.98,0:19:11.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.28,0:19:16.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I thought I'd collect some driftwood\nand have a campfire.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.75,0:19:19.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?! Are you an idiot?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.25,0:19:20.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There's no point!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.49,0:19:22.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Nobody's interested in that kind of thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.69,0:19:23.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.03,0:20:00.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.78,0:20:20.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.73,0:20:37.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Give me a break... Well, what can you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.05,0:20:55.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Thanks to you, I remembered the original\npurpose of this off meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.92,0:20:57.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.55,0:20:59.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The purpose?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.79,0:21:06.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.89,0:21:10.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The reason we all gathered together\nin a place like this
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.13,0:21:16.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,was that we thought we'd spend at least\nthe last day of our lives pleasantly.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.90,0:21:19.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ah, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.71,0:21:21.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.08,0:21:23.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,"The last day of our lives"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.11,0:21:24.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This... This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.95,0:21:30.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hitomi may be taking part in this\noff meeting with Sato!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.75,0:21:32.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Off meeting?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.09,0:21:37.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The Island Nearest to Paradise?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.83,0:21:38.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\c&H050505&\shad0\bord0\frz16.41\pos(219,194)}Let's terminate our lives,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.33,0:21:43.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.53,0:21:48.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,They intend to end their lives today!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.74,0:21:56.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Se... Senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.86,0:21:59.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\c&H5A99F8&\bord2.3\shad0\3c&H000000&\fscx156.25\fscy176.25\pos(193,92)}Episode 12
