Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.07,0:23:33.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're a hikikomori, more pathetic than a stray dog!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.14,0:23:35.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's already too late to turn back.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.08,0:23:36.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This is a conspiracy.
